workflow.name: Automate YouTube Content Strategy with AI, Apify & Google Sheets
workflow.description:
## üìå Overview

This advanced multi-phase n8n workflow automates the complete research, analysis, and ideation pipeline for a YouTube strategist. It scrapes competitor channels, analyzes top-performing titles and thumbnails, identifies niche trends, gathers audience sentiment from comments, and produces data-driven content ideas‚Äîautomatically writing them into a structured Google Sheets dashboard.

This system is ideal for:

* YouTube creators
* Agencies
* Content strategists
* Automation engineers
* Anyone who wants to generate YouTube content ideas backed by real data

---

# üß† High‚ÄëLevel Architecture

The workflow is split into **5 phases**, each building on the previous:

### **Phase 1 ‚Äî Niche Outliers (Input: User Form)**

Scrapes 3 high‚Äëquality channels from your niche, extracts their outlier videos, and analyzes why they work.

### **Phase 2 ‚Äî Broad Niche Insights (Weekly)**

Scrapes the top trending content in your broad niche (e.g., "AI", "fitness", "personal finance") and logs weekly insights.

### **Phase 3 ‚Äî Niche Insights (Daily)**

Scrapes the top videos in your specific micro‚Äëniche daily to keep track of content momentum.

### **Phase 4 ‚Äî Comment Analysis**

Analyzes real comments from your channel to understand what your audience likes, dislikes, and wants more of.

### **Phase 5 ‚Äî Content Ideation**

Generates 3 highly‚Äëoptimized title + thumbnail concepts using all prior insights.

Everything is automatically logged into a Google Sheets dashboard.

---

# üß© Phase-by-Phase Breakdown

## ‚≠ê **Phase 1 ‚Äî Niche Outliers (Form Trigger)**

1. User enters **3 YouTube channel URLs** in a form.
2. Workflow scrapes each channel using **Apify YouTube Scraper**.
3. Filters for top-performing videos.
4. Extracts: title, views, likes, thumbnail, URL.
5. AI analyzes:

   * Power words in titles (OpenRouter/GPT 4.1-mini)
   * Thumbnail attention hooks (OpenAI Vision)
6. All insights are appended into the **‚ÄúNiche Outliers‚Äù** sheet.

**Purpose:** Understand what the best creators in your niche are doing.

---

## üåê **Phase 2 ‚Äî Broad Niche Insights (Weekly ‚Äî Sundays @ 5 AM)**

1. Workflow scrapes the top videos for a **broad niche** (e.g., ‚Äúartificial intelligence‚Äù).
2. Analyzes:

   * Title structure
   * Power words
   * Thumbnail cues
3. Writes weekly insights to **‚ÄúBroad Niche Weekly‚Äù** sheet.

**Purpose:** Stay informed about macro‚Äëlevel trends.

---

## üéØ **Phase 3 ‚Äî Niche Insights (Daily @ 6 AM)**

1. Scrapes the top videos in your **specific micro‚Äëniche** (e.g., ‚Äún8n automations‚Äù).
2. Runs title + thumbnail analysis.
3. Appends daily results to **‚ÄúNiche Daily‚Äù**.
4. Results feed directly into Phase 5.

**Purpose:** Track daily momentum and trending formats.

---

## üí¨ **Phase 4 ‚Äî Comment Analysis (Channel Feedback)**

1. Scrapes your channel‚Äôs **latest 5 videos**.
2. Extracts up to **30 comments** from each.
3. Aggregates comments.
4. AI identifies:

   * What viewers love
   * What viewers dislike
   * What viewers are asking for
5. Stores patterns in **‚ÄúComment Analysis‚Äù** sheet.

**Purpose:** Understand real audience demand.

---

## üí° **Phase 5 ‚Äî Content Ideation Using AI**

Using insights from all previous phases:

* Top titles
* Power words
* Thumbnail patterns
* Daily niche trends
* Audience comment analysis
* Channel positioning

The **Creative Agent** produces:

* 3 optimized video titles
* 3 matching thumbnail concepts

These are appended to the **‚ÄúIdeation‚Äù** sheet.

A Slack notification is sent when ideation is ready.

**Purpose:** Fully automated content idea generation.

---

# üóÇÔ∏è Outputs in Google Sheets

The workflow populates these tabs:

### **üìå Niche Outliers** (top competitor videos)

### **üìå Broad Niche Weekly** (weekly trend analysis)

### **üìå Niche Daily** (daily trend analysis)

### **üìå Comment Analysis** (audience sentiment)

### **üìå Ideation** (final titles + thumbnails)

---

# üîß What This Workflow Automates

‚úî Competitor analysis
‚úî Thumbnail + title breakdowns
‚úî Daily niche tracking
‚úî Weekly niche tracking
‚úî Viewer sentiment analysis
‚úî Fully AI‚Äëgenerated content ideas
‚úî Automatic data logging to Google Sheets
‚úî Slack notifications

This is essentially a **24/7 AI YouTube strategist**.

---

# ‚öôÔ∏è Setup Requirements

* **Apify API Key** (used in 5 scraper nodes)
* **OpenRouter API Key** (for GPT 4.1-mini intelligence)
* **OpenAI API Key** (for thumbnail image analysis)
* **Google Sheets OAuth2 Credential**
* Make a copy of the provided sheet template
* Fill Set nodes:

  * Phase II: Broad niche (e.g., "AI")
  * Phase III: Micro niche (e.g., "n8n automations")
  * Phase IV: Your Channel URL
  * Phase V: Your Channel Description

---

# üß™ Testing Guide

1. Test the **Form Trigger** with 3 competitor channel URLs.
2. Test both **Schedule Triggers** (weekly + daily) manually.
3. Verify Sheets are receiving rows.
4. Run the full pipeline end‚Äëto‚Äëend.
5. Confirm Slack notification.

Everything should chain together smoothly.

---

# üéâ Final Result

By the end of this workflow, you have a:

### üß† **Data‚Äëdriven YouTube strategy system**

that:

* studies your niche
* finds outliers
* understands your audience
* detects trends
* generates smart content ideas every day

data.details: The Filter node can be used to filter items based on a condition. If the condition is met, the item will be passed on to the next node. If the condition is not met, the item will be omitted. Conditions can be combined together by AND(meet all conditions), or OR(meet at least one condition).
